name: Inner Conflict - Nachhause - CD
description:
'Nachhause' by the fantastic, female-fronted German punk band INNER CONFLICT.

This great band have it all, anger, melody, pace and a punk rock sound that'll appeal to all fans of punk.

The CD is only £3 and postage and packaging is FREE in the UK.

Tack listing:
01 Der Rücken ist im Arsch
02 Dom
03 Siebenmeilenstiefel
04 Totensund
05 Lauter als die Angst
06 Ab jetzt
07 Mal sehen
08 Einen Tag am Strand
09 Sofa vs. Schleudertrauma
10 Hand in Hand
11 The best of Wahrheit
12 Espon

name: CONTEMPT AND R.A.M-M.A.N SPLIT ALBUM - 12" VINYL & FREE CD
description: 19 tracks of UK punk rock. This split between R.A.M-M.A.N and Contempt is available on 12" vinyl with a FREE CD!!! (not a CDR, an industry standard CD in printed card wallet)..... OR, you get a CD with a free 12", depending on what you prefer :)
